flowchart TD
    %% Google Voice Service Data Flow Map
    %% Derived from 310 captured HTTP requests + 3 streams

    Browser([Browser / Web Client])

    subgraph Google Voice Backend
        VoiceAPI[clients6.google.com<br/>Voice REST API<br/>26 endpoints]
        RingGroups[voice.clients6.google.com<br/>RingGroupsService gRPC]
        SIPGateway[web.voice.telephony.goog<br/>SIP-over-WebSocket<br/>Call signaling]
        MediaServer[74.125.39.x<br/>OGHP Media Gateway<br/>RTP/SRTP audio]
    end

    subgraph Google Shared Services
        People[people*.clients6.google.com<br/>PeopleStack / Contacts<br/>Autocomplete + Groups]
        WAA[waa-pa.clients6.google.com<br/>Web Activity Audit]
        AsyncData[ogads-pa.clients6.google.com<br/>OneGoogle AsyncData]
        Signaler[signaler-pa.clients6.google.com<br/>Punctual Push Server]
    end

    subgraph Infrastructure
        STUN[stun.l.google.com:19302<br/>STUN Server]
        ReCAPTCHA[www.google.com<br/>reCAPTCHA Enterprise]
        Analytics[play.google.com<br/>Logging / Telemetry]
    end

    Browser -->|REST POST /voice/v1/*| VoiceAPI
    Browser -->|gRPC /$rpc/google.voice.*| RingGroups
    Browser -->|WebSocket SIP| SIPGateway
    Browser -->|RTP/SRTP Opus| MediaServer
    Browser -->|gRPC /$rpc/peoplestack.*| People
    Browser -->|gRPC /$rpc/google.internal.waa.*| WAA
    Browser -->|gRPC /$rpc/google.internal.onegoogle.*| AsyncData
    Browser -->|REST /punctual/v1/*| Signaler
    Browser -->|STUN Binding| STUN
    Browser -->|POST /recaptcha/*| ReCAPTCHA
    Browser -->|POST /log, /g/collect| Analytics

    SIPGateway -.->|SDP offer/answer| MediaServer
    STUN -.->|SRFLX candidate| MediaServer

